Ah, it's me. I'm feeling energetic today, Laura. What's
going on, Luna? I want to talk to you, Vita. Let's hang out
together, okay? Hey, big sister, what's up?
What's wrong, you seem a bit down, Luna...?

I'm sorry, but I can't understand what you're saying. Could
you please clarify, Laura? Since I'm still new, could you
guide me, Lunaroa? Thank you, Vega. I'm trying my best to
assist, Vita.

Byo, byouinna ra.... Don'na, byouki demo, nan demo nao serun
da. ... Doushita? Nande, sonname de, o, ore o miru...?
Why!!! With such a name!!! To see me!!!
